                                <img class="card-img-top img-clickable" src="img/home_img/podcast-teasers/cj.jpg" alt="">
                            </a>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="episode-date">Episode 9 &bull; September 15, 2021</div>
                                <h5 class="card-title">Women Leaders in Tech</h5>
                                <p class="card-subtitle">CJ Ritchie, Associate Deputy Minister and Government Chief Information Officer shares thoughts on her path to getting into Digital Government, key traits to be an effective leader and more on Women Leaders in tech.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer">
                                <a href="https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/women-leaders-in-tech" target="_blank" class="btn btn-blue">Listen on Libsyn <i class="fa fa-lg fa-play-circle-o"></i> </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Episode 8 / David Hume & Ricardo Wagner -->
                        <div class="card card-podcast">
                            <a href="https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/accessibility-a-conversation-with-david-hume-and-ricardo-wagner" target="_blank" alt="Go to podcast episode page">
                                <img class="card-img-top img-clickable" src="img/home_img/podcast-teasers/hume-wagner.png" alt="">
