                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer">
                                <a href="https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/accessibility-a-conversation-with-david-hume-and-ricardo-wagner" target="_blank" class="btn btn-blue">Listen on Libsyn <i class="fa fa-lg fa-play-circle-o"></i>
