            </div>
            <div class="row pt-5 pb-3">
                <div class="col">
                    <h4>How to Subscribe</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row text-white-50">
                <div class="col-sm pr-sm-5">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                        <div><img class="podcast-icon" src="img/Icons/Podcasts_(iOS).svg"></div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 ml-3">iOS</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p>Open the Podcasts app on your phone:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tap the LIBRARY button at the bottom of your app</li>
                        <li>Choose the option ADD A PODCAST BY URL and enter the RSS link: <span class="text-blue">https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/rss</span>
                        <li>Tap SUBSCRIBE</li>
                        <li>Tap the DONE button at the top right</li>
                        <li>Tap on The Exchange Podcast logo to access the episodes</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm pl-sm-5">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                        <img class="podcast-icon" src="img/Icons/Google_Podcasts_icon.svg">
                        <h5 class="mb-0 ml-3">Android</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p>Visit the Google Play Store to find a podcast player that suits you. These steps should be similar in all applications:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Tap on the + sign at the top right of the screen</li>
                        <li>Select "Add an RSS Feed"</li>
                        <li>Enter the RSS link: <span class="text-blue">https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/rss</span>
                        <li>Tap "Add"</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="row text-white-50">
                <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-6 m-auto">
                    <p>If using another podcast application, subscribe by visiting <a href="https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/" target="_blank">https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/</a> and clicking the RSS icon, or entering the RSS link: <span class="text-blue">https://bcdevexchange.libsyn.com/rss</span>
